statements: SELECT * FROM vehicle_performance_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE acceleration > 5;
SELECT fuel_consumption FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE speed < 60 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE fuel_consumption BETWEEN 5.5 AND 7.5;
SELECT vehicle_id, acceleration, speed FROM vehicle_performance_data ORDER BY acceleration DESC, speed ASC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE fuel_consumption > 10 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed, acceleration FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE speed > 100 AND acceleration > 5 ORDER BY acceleration DESC, speed ASC;
SELECT timestamp, speed FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY speed DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE acceleration < 0 ORDER BY vehicle_id ASC, acceleration DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT vehicle_id FROM vehicle_performance_data WHERE speed < 50 ORDER BY vehicle_id;
SELECT * FROM VehicleData WHERE vehicle_id = 1;
SELECT speed, acceleration FROM VehicleData WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_level FROM VehicleData ORDER BY fuel_level DESC;
SELECT * FROM PerformanceMetrics WHERE engine_temperature < 100;
SELECT metric_id, tire_pressure FROM PerformanceMetrics WHERE vehicle_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM VehicleData WHERE speed > 50 ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT vehicle_id, acceleration FROM VehicleData WHERE fuel_level < 50 ORDER BY acceleration ASC
SELECT vehicle_id, speed, acceleration FROM VehicleData WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-01-31' ORDER BY speed DESC
SELECT * FROM VehicleData WHERE speed BETWEEN 60 AND 80 AND acceleration > 5 ORDER BY timestamp ASC

SELECT vehicle_id, timestamp, engine_temperature FROM VehicleData JOIN PerformanceMetrics ON VehicleData.vehicle_id = PerformanceMetrics.vehicle_id WHERE engine_temperature > 90 ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT * FROM vehicles;
SELECT vehicle_name, mileage FROM vehicles WHERE vehicle_type = 'SUV';
SELECT vehicle_id, manufacture_date FROM vehicles ORDER BY manufacture_date DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, vehicle_name, vehicle_type FROM vehicles WHERE mileage > 50000;
SELECT vehicle_id, vehicle_name, manufacture_date FROM vehicles WHERE manufacture_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM vehicles ORDER BY vehicle_name DESC, manufacture_date ASC;
SELECT vehicle_name, vehicle_type, manufacture_date FROM vehicles WHERE mileage > 50000;

SELECT v.vehicle_name, v.vehicle_type, p.speed, p.fuel_consumption FROM vehicles v JOIN vehicle_performance_data p ON v.vehicle_id = p.vehicle_id WHERE p.timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY p.speed DESC;
SELECT v.vehicle_name, v.vehicle_type, l.latitude, l.longitude FROM vehicles v JOIN vehicle_location_data l ON v.vehicle_id = l.vehicle_id WHERE l.timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';

SELECT v.vehicle_name, v.manufacture_date, p.engine_temperature, l.latitude, l.longitude FROM vehicles v JOIN vehicle_performance_data p ON v.vehicle_id = p.vehicle_id JOIN vehicle_location_data l ON v.vehicle_id = l.vehicle_id WHERE p.speed > 100 AND l.longitude < -90;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, engine_temp, speed FROM vehicle_data WHERE fuel_level > 50;
SELECT location, vehicle_id FROM vehicle_data ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_log WHERE maintenance_type = 'Oil Change';
SELECT trip_distance, start_timestamp, end_timestamp FROM trip_data WHERE start_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM vehicle_data WHERE speed > 100 ORDER BY engine_temp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT vehicle_id, engine_temp, fuel_level FROM vehicle_data WHERE fuel_level < 0.25;
SELECT log_id, maintenance_type, mechanic_name, notes FROM maintenance_log WHERE maintenance_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT trip_id, vehicle_id, trip_distance FROM trip_data ORDER BY start_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT driver_id, driver_name, license_number FROM driver_data WHERE contact_number LIKE '%555%' ORDER BY driver_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM VehicleData;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed, mileage FROM VehicleData WHERE speed > 50;
SELECT * FROM LocationData ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, latitude, longitude FROM LocationData WHERE latitude < 40 AND longitude > -100;
SELECT driver_name, driver_license FROM DriverData WHERE driver_name LIKE 'John%';
SELECT * FROM VehicleData WHERE speed > 100;
SELECT vehicle_id, timestamp, mileage FROM VehicleData ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT location_id, vehicle_id, latitude, longitude FROM LocationData WHERE latitude BETWEEN 40.0 AND 45.0;
SELECT engine_id, vehicle_id, temperature, fuel_level FROM EngineData WHERE fuel_level < 0.2 ORDER BY temperature ASC;
SELECT driver_name, driver_license FROM DriverData WHERE vehicle_id = 3;
